name: Magic forest no sleep x Neil Ewing

metadata.description:
Magic forest no sleep x Neil Ewing

NoSleep Featured artist Neil Ewing . Showcase his "Honorary Freaks by Bombastic Plastic" Exhibition at FuzzyBean Gallery.

We also launching our collab drop! bring fuzzy and weird to Magic forest and Bombastic Plastic community.

ABOUT BOMBASTIC PLASTIC
Bombastic Plastic is a creative company founded in 2018 by Neil Ewing, a multimedia artist and designer from Colorado.

The goal of Bombastic Plastic is to create art and objects driven by nostalgia, personal narrative and humor.

1/ Supply: 500
2/ Free claim. each wallet can mint 2
3/ "Magic forest no sleep" and "Bombastic Plastic" holders only
4/ Snapshot on Jan 13
5/ Royalties will 100% support artist Neil Ewing toys project
